/-- This is a technical result to ensure that the image of the `‚ÑÇ`-basis of `‚ÑÇ^n` defined in
`canonicalEmbedding.latticeBasis` is a `‚Ñù`-basis of `‚Ñù^r‚ÇÅ √ó ‚ÑÇ^r‚ÇÇ`,
